## Phase 2: Development

**Gate Check:**
```
IF checkpoint in ["DEV_COMPLETE", "QA_APPROVED", "STAGING_COMPLETE"]:
  Skip development (already complete)
ELSE:
  Execute development
```

**Invoke Skill:**

**Context for skill:**
- Story content loaded via @file reference above
